title: Victoria : The First 150 Years
creator_credit: Gas and Fuel Corporation of Victoria
brief_description: An overview of Victoria covering its history, culture and landscape. Gold, sport, bushfires and rural Victoria are amongst the subjects covered and there is also a significant use of historical film footage in this description of Victoria.
